OL,3,CParents welcome court ruling that use
OL,4,Cof unisex toilets at school was
OL,5,Cunlawful
OL,7,FParents who were locked in a two-year
OL,8,Fbattle with Scottish Borders Council
OL,9,Fover the use of gender neutral toilets
OL,10,Fat Earlston Primary School say the
OL,11,Fordeal forced them to take their son
OL,12,Fout of school.
OL,14,FYesterday, a judge ruled that state
OL,15,Fschools in Scotland must provide
OL,16,Fsingle-sex toilets for pupils
OL,17,Ffollowing a legal challenge brought by
OL,18,Fparents against Scottish Borders
OL,19,FCouncil.
