OL,3,CParents welcome court ruling that use
OL,4,Cof unisex toilets at school was
OL,5,Cunlawful
OL,7,FThe authority had installed gender
OL,8,Fneutral toilets at the school.
OL,10,FParents Leigh Hurley and Sean
OL,11,FStratford, whose child attended the
OL,12,Fschool, complained to the authority
OL,13,Fabout the use of the toilets, the
OL,14,Fpunishment of children who "misgender"
OL,15,Fothers and about an issue relating to
OL,16,Ftrans children participating in sports
OL,17,Fday.
