OL,3,CParents welcome court ruling that use
OL,4,Cof unisex toilets at school was
OL,5,Cunlawful
OL,7,FAll three issues were initially
OL,8,Frejected, however, the lawyer
OL,9,Frepresenting them, Rosie Walker,
OL,10,Flodged a petition for review in
OL,11,FJanuary.
OL,13,FA court order, known as a declarator,
OL,14,Fis set to be issued by Judge Lady Ross
OL,15,FKC to ensure the legal obligations of
OL,16,FScottish state schools are clear.
OL,18,FScottish Borders Council accepted the
OL,19,Fdecision.
