OL,3,CParents welcome court ruling that use
OL,4,Cof unisex toilets at school was
OL,5,Cunlawful
OL,7,FIt follows a decision by the Supreme
OL,8,FCourt on 16 April which ruled that
OL,9,F"woman" and "sex" in the Equality Act
OL,10,Frefer to a biological woman and
OL,11,Fbiological sex.
OL,13,FDelivering the judgement, Judge Lord
OL,14,FHodge said the "central question" is
OL,15,Fhow the words "woman" and "sex" are
OL,16,Fdefined in the 2010 Equality Act.
