OL,3,CParents welcome court ruling that use
OL,4,Cof unisex toilets at school was
OL,5,Cunlawful
OL,7,FHe said: "Do these terms refer to
OL,8,Fbiological woman or biological sex, or
OL,9,Fis a woman to be interpreted as
OL,10,Fextending to a trans woman with a
OL,11,FGender Recognition Certificate (GRC)?
OL,13,F"The unanimous decision of this court
OL,14,Fis that the terms woman and sex in the
OL,15,FEquality Act 2010 refer to a
OL,16,Fbiological woman and biological sex."
OL,18,FLeigh Hurley and Sean Stratford were
OL,19,Fsupported in bringing their case in
OL,20,Fthe Court of Session in Edinburgh by
OL,21,FFor Women Scotland.
