OL,7,F'I'm sorry if anyone was made to feel
OL,8,Funcomfortable'
OL,10,FSpeaking on behalf of Scottish Borders
OL,11,FCouncil, Cllr Julie Pirone apologised
OL,12,Fto parents.
OL,14,FThe family's lawyer believes the case
OL,15,Fwill have "far-reaching implications".
