OL,3,CParents welcome court ruling that use
OL,4,Cof unisex toilets at school was
OL,5,Cunlawful
OL,7,FRosie Walker, head of litigation at
OL,8,FGilson Gray solicitors, said: "All
OL,9,Fschools in Scotland will now have to
OL,10,Flook again at whether their toilets
OL,11,Fcomply with the School Premises
OL,12,F(General Requirements and Standards)
OL,13,F(Scotland) Regulations 1967, which
OL,14,Frequire half of school toilet
OL,15,Ffacilities to be for boys and half for
OL,16,Fgirls.
OL,18,F"This case, on top of the Supreme
OL,19,FCourt decision last week, gives focus
OL,20,Fto the importance of protecting sex
OL,21,Fbased rights and single sex spaces."
